www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/billy-idol-joan-jett@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/billy-idol-joan-jett@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-idol">比利·偶像 (Billy Idol)</a>宣布今年将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joan-jett">琼·杰特 (Joan Jett)</a>进行全新的北美巡演 - 请查看下面的完整巡演日期列表。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/joan-jett-blackhearts-new-album-changeup-ted-nugent-miley-cyrus-taylor-hawkins-3215547">琼·杰特：“泰德·纽金特的批评？这就是我一生所面对的问题——被注销”</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨天（1月21日），比利·偶像在社交媒体上宣布了这次巡演，这次巡演被称为<em>“It&#39;s A Nice Day To…Tour Again！”</em> 。它将分两部分进行——第一部分在春季，第二部分在夏季。 </p><figure id="attachment_3817767" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3817767" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3817767" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Billy-Idol@2000x1270.jpg" alt="比利·爱多尔 (Billy Idol) 将于 2024 年登台表演。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Billy-Idol@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Billy-Idol@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Billy-Idol@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Billy-Idol@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Billy-Idol@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Billy-Idol@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3817767" class="wp-caption-text">比利·爱多尔 (Billy Idol) 将于 2024 年登台表演。图片来源：Dia Dipasupil/Getty Images for 摇滚名人堂</figcaption></figure><p>到目前为止，《美国偶像》已经宣布了 30 场演出，所有这些节目都将包括琼·杰特 (Joan Jett) 和她的乐队 The Blackhearts。第一轮巡演将于4月30日至5月23日期间进行，第二轮巡演将于8月16日至9月25日期间进行。</p><p>为了宣布这次巡演，《偶像》拍摄了喜剧演员马特·莱夫 (Matt Rife) 主演的短剧。在咖啡店点饮料时，《偶像》由饰演咖啡师的 Rife 为他服务。莱夫表示“今天是喝白摩卡的好日子”，这促使比利·爱多尔考虑再次上路。</p><p>在接下来的几天里，偶像到处都能听到莱夫的声音，并最终与他的治疗师（琼·杰特饰演）交谈。当他向她寻求建议时，琼告诉他“这是再次巡演的好日子”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DFF3yUigZaO/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.